com.bergerkiller.bukkit.common.map

Class MCSDGenCiede2000

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.bergerkiller.bukkit.common.map.color.MapColorSpaceData
      • com.bergerkiller.bukkit.common.map.MCSDGenCiede2000
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable

    public class MCSDGenCiede2000
extends MapColorSpaceData
    This class is used to generate the RGB<>Color transformation mapping. It uses some pretty sophisticated and slow maths, but because it's run once and then stored as a binary blob this does not matter.

    This generator generates the best matching map color for all RGB color values available, with an index table from map color to RGB. It uses the ciede2000 color differencing algorithm.
